76561198024218344,Recommended,270550,26073588,"Posted: 16 October, 2016",all,Gaming Raz,"Was given a coupon for this game which made the price $0.69WELL OKAY!It's time for....Yet Another Zombie Defencegame review.This is a basic zombie defence game that packs the fun!First you choose one of three characters. Then you are thrown into an arena, with one street lamp and you begin with a pistol.Each round intensifies with hordes of Zombies charging after you. The first and sceond round are easily completed with just a pistol in this top down view of a game and as you take down the zombies, they drop bonus items and monies to buy more weapons and defence. Such as barriers, turrets, mines, etc, etc. to help slow down and hold back the Zombie horde.And it works!Simple but fun Zombie shooting time!There is online standings, coop and 4 player death match. All just add to the fun. Although you might find it difficult to find other online players at times.So for a $1.99 or less, this is a fun little Zombie shooter!Get it! Before the Zombies get you!"
