,Recommended,270550,28768598,"Posted: 28 December, 2016",all,AMCMaster,"OVERVIEWYet Another Zombie Defense is a defense building action game developed and published by Awesome Games Studio. The whole concept is that you are a human that is being overrun by zombies night after night, Every night you survive you will have money to allow for you to upgrade weapons, get palisades and buy turrets. The goal is to survive as long as possible with or without the help of friends.PROS+ Easy Achievements+ Steam Trading Cards+ Co-op+ Multiplayer+ Fun+ Cheap+ Easy to RunCONS- Not The Best Graphics- No Save FeatureCONCLUSIONThis game is a big bang for you buck. It has a fun and easy concept that allows for you to get sucked in very easily and can become very strategic over time. I do have to admit it is a hell of a lot more fun when you have other people to play with. Although it might not be much to look at, and not too much to come back to, the fun I had in this game with a few friends really allowed for it to be a hidden gem.7.5/10"
