y join your game and not agree how you spend money which may become problematic as a teamSome things I wish would be changed:upgradable weapons and barriers, option to change leader, minor glitches fixed (I've experienced two so far: one where the camera will stick and won't follow your character anymore and when your character freezes at the end of a round and either won't move or shoot until you die)"
