r, extra health, regen, walk speed, etc.The public online mode of also horrid, unless your the host you cant build, buy, or pickup items. All you can do i shoot using the same starter pistol with infinite bullets that takes 2 clips to kill a zombie with.There are also a few powerups that drop that make you invisable for a short time or make you reload faster for a couple seconds.Also you get to choose from 'Guy' 'Girl' and 'SWAT' as playable characters.But for the price its a well made game and it will probably kill a few minutes of bordem or maybe a few hours if you get creative with a few friends."
